c0000000
00:00:01.170 --> 00:00:04.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[camera shutters clicking]</b></Default>

c0000001
00:00:04.920 --> 00:00:07.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I am terribly sorry that
my actions have caused such</b></Default>

c0000002
00:00:07.260 --> 00:00:08.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>a commotion lately.</b></Default>

c0000003
00:00:09.220 --> 00:00:11.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- What kind of person
is this boyfriend?</b></Default>

c0000004
00:00:11.640 --> 00:00:13.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- And how did the two
of you end up dating?</b></Default>

c0000005
00:00:13.890 --> 00:00:15.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- He attends the same
high school as me</b></Default>

c0000006
00:00:15.680 --> 00:00:17.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and happens to be
a year younger.</b></Default>

c0000007
00:00:17.430 --> 00:00:18.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He confessed his love
to me in front</b></Default>

c0000008
00:00:19.020 --> 00:00:21.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>of the whole school and he--</b></Default>

c0000009
00:00:21.360 --> 00:00:24.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Miss Mai, excuse me, but your
face seems to have turned red.</b></Default>

c0000010
00:00:25.780 --> 00:00:27.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I'm talking about
my first boyfriend here,</b></Default>

c0000011
00:00:28.070 --> 00:00:30.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and it's in front of all kinds
 of different people and camera.</b></Default>

c0000012
00:00:30.860 --> 00:00:32.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think anyone would
be embarrassed in my shoes.</b></Default>

c0000013
00:00:33.080 --> 00:00:34.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[both laughing]</b></Default>

c0000014
00:00:34.410 --> 00:00:35.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [grunts]
- This was an important</b></Default>

c0000015
00:00:35.740 --> 00:00:36.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>movie production announcement</b></Default>

c0000016
00:00:36.950 --> 00:00:38.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but it's turned into this.</b></Default>

c0000017
00:00:38.290 --> 00:00:39.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've caused trouble
for the director</b></Default>

c0000018
00:00:39.960 --> 00:00:42.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and my costars.
I'm truly sorry.</b></Default>

c0000019
00:00:42.460 --> 00:00:44.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- The producer said thanks
to this he won't need</b></Default>

c0000020
00:00:44.630 --> 00:00:47.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to do advertising himself
so there's no problem.</b></Default>

c0000021
00:00:47.170 --> 00:00:49.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]
[all laughing]</b></Default>

c0000022
00:00:49.300 --> 00:00:51.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Actually, my boyfriend's
a big part of the reason</b></Default>

c0000023
00:00:51.890 --> 00:00:53.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I chose to continue
with showbiz.</b></Default>

c0000024
00:00:53.640 --> 00:00:55.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If I had never met him,</b></Default>

c0000025
00:00:55.640 --> 00:00:57.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b> I don't believe I would have hd
the opportunity</b></Default>

c0000026
00:00:58.060 --> 00:00:59.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to appear on camera
like this again.</b></Default>

c0000027
00:01:02.060 --> 00:01:05.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b> I don't mind you trying to peer
into my own private life,</b></Default>

c0000028
00:01:05.230 --> 00:01:08.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but he's an ordinary guy who
didn't sign up for all this.</b></Default>

c0000029
00:01:08.240 --> 00:01:12.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b> I ask you to respect his privay
if at all possible, please.</b></Default>

c0000030
00:01:12.280 --> 00:01:14.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Nice. Just way too cool!
[cat meows]</b></Default>

c0000031
00:01:14.830 --> 00:01:16.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Secretly taking pictures
and shamelessly putting</b></Default>

c0000032
00:01:17.040 --> 00:01:18.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>them online without consent
isn't something</b></Default>

c0000033
00:01:18.830 --> 00:01:20.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that ever happens
in this country,</b></Default>

c0000034
00:01:20.250 --> 00:01:22.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so you're fine.
- [laughing]</b></Default>

c0000035
00:01:23.170 --> 00:01:25.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Kaede needs to do her best
for big brother as well.</b></Default>

c0000036
00:01:30.670 --> 00:01:33.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [singing in Japanese]</b></Default>

c0000037
00:01:33.680 --> 00:01:36.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[The Peggies' "Kimi no sei"]</b></Default>

c0000038
00:01:36.640 --> 00:01:43.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪ ♪</b></Default>

c0000039
00:02:18.930 --> 00:02:25.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪ ♪</b></Default>

c0000040
00:02:45.250 --> 00:02:52.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪ ♪</b></Default>

c0000041
00:03:01.640 --> 00:03:03.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I'm glad it didn't turn into
as big of an ordeal</b></Default>

c0000042
00:03:03.850 --> 00:03:04.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>as I thought it would.</b></Default>

c0000043
00:03:04.940 --> 00:03:05.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's all thanks to what</b></Default>

c0000044
00:03:05.980 --> 00:03:06.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the director said.</b></Default>

c0000045
00:03:07.020 --> 00:03:08.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I mean, sure, there's that,</b></Default>

c0000046
00:03:08.770 --> 00:03:11.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but I think it's mostly because
you handled the press conference</b></Default>

c0000047
00:03:11.230 --> 00:03:12.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>with so much grace.</b></Default>

c0000048
00:03:12.480 --> 00:03:14.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Your reactions were pure.</b></Default>

c0000049
00:03:14.190 --> 00:03:15.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You were really adorable.</b></Default>

c0000050
00:03:16.280 --> 00:03:18.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How did I get so lucky?</b></Default>

c0000051
00:03:18.120 --> 00:03:20.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Having you
as my girlfriend makes me</b></Default>

c0000052
00:03:20.330 --> 00:03:21.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the world's happiest guy.</b></Default>

c0000053
00:03:22.040 --> 00:03:25.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Well, of course it does but
once the movie starts filming,</b></Default>

c0000054
00:03:25.620 --> 00:03:27.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll be crazy busy again.</b></Default>

c0000055
00:03:27.420 --> 00:03:29.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Even then it won't
change how I feel.</b></Default>

c0000056
00:03:30.000 --> 00:03:31.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I really don't think there's
any guy out there</b></Default>

c0000057
00:03:31.880 --> 00:03:33.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that's happier than me.</b></Default>

c0000058
00:03:34.210 --> 00:03:35.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey, what about you?</b></Default>

c0000059
00:03:36.680 --> 00:03:38.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You know what, Sakuta?</b></Default>

c0000060
00:03:38.430 --> 00:03:40.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Yeah, what is it?</b></Default>

c0000061
00:03:40.260 --> 00:03:44.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I bet that you don't actually
know how in love with you I am.</b></Default>

c0000062
00:03:44.600 --> 00:03:46.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [grunts]
Nah.</b></Default>

c0000063
00:03:46.390 --> 00:03:48.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There's no way
I don't love you more.</b></Default>

c0000064
00:03:48.350 --> 00:03:50.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Yeah, yeah. I'll just let
you believe that for now.</b></Default>

c0000065
00:03:51.650 --> 00:03:52.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>See you later, then.</b></Default>

c0000066
00:03:56.030 --> 00:03:57.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [exhales]</b></Default>

c0000067
00:04:03.950 --> 00:04:04.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hmm?</b></Default>

c0000068
00:04:08.580 --> 00:04:09.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000069
00:04:12.710 --> 00:04:14.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[cat purrs]
Come to think of it,</b></Default>

c0000070
00:04:14.710 --> 00:04:16.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Makinohara hasn't
been around lately, huh?</b></Default>

c0000071
00:04:16.970 --> 00:04:19.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Kaede's a little worried
about her, too.</b></Default>

c0000072
00:04:19.430 --> 00:04:21.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And Hayate seems kinda lonely.</b></Default>

c0000073
00:04:21.760 --> 00:04:23.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- The fact that she signed
her name "Shoko-san" means</b></Default>

c0000074
00:04:24.010 --> 00:04:25.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b> that this letter wasn't written
by</b></Default>

c0000075
00:04:25.600 --> 00:04:26.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the middle
school-aged Makinohara.</b></Default>

c0000076
00:04:28.230 --> 00:04:29.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Which means it has to be...</b></Default>

c0000077
00:04:32.060 --> 00:04:33.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey, Futaba.</b></Default>

c0000078
00:04:33.610 --> 00:04:36.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Azusagawa,
how many times is this?</b></Default>

c0000079
00:04:36.320 --> 00:04:39.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I didn't come seeking council
for puberty syndrome this time.</b></Default>

c0000080
00:04:39.490 --> 00:04:41.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, actually, it might be kind
of adjacent to it, but...</b></Default>

c0000081
00:04:42.370 --> 00:04:43.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Hmm?</b></Default>

c0000082
00:04:44.490 --> 00:04:46.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- It's a letter I got
from Shoko-san.</b></Default>

c0000083
00:04:46.540 --> 00:04:48.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- And when is this "tomorrow?"</b></Default>

c0000084
00:04:48.410 --> 00:04:50.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Today, I think.</b></Default>

c0000085
00:04:50.370 --> 00:04:52.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Did you say anything
to Sakurajima yet?</b></Default>

c0000086
00:04:52.170 --> 00:04:53.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I didn't.</b></Default>

c0000087
00:04:53.500 --> 00:04:55.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- So what you're asking me
for today is how</b></Default>

c0000088
00:04:55.630 --> 00:04:57.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to avoid getting
caught cheating?</b></Default>

c0000089
00:04:57.260 --> 00:04:58.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- No, of course not.</b></Default>

c0000090
00:04:58.550 --> 00:04:59.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don't make weird presumptions.</b></Default>

c0000091
00:05:00.050 --> 00:05:01.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Then why didn't you
just tell her?</b></Default>

c0000092
00:05:01.800 --> 00:05:04.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Hmm. Well, how do you think I
should go about bringing it up?</b></Default>

c0000093
00:05:04.760 --> 00:05:06.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Huh. It's strange
for you to worry</b></Default>

c0000094
00:05:06.680 --> 00:05:08.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>about something like that
in the first place, though.</b></Default>

c0000095
00:05:08.600 --> 00:05:11.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Usually you'd tell her ASAP
so she's scold you</b></Default>

c0000096
00:05:11.520 --> 00:05:12.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>since that's a reward
for you, right?</b></Default>

c0000097
00:05:13.020 --> 00:05:14.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- What kind of person
do you think I am?</b></Default>

c0000098
00:05:14.980 --> 00:05:17.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- A rascal who has
a masochistic streak.</b></Default>

c0000099
00:05:17.110 --> 00:05:18.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Yeah, I shouldn't
have asked that.</b></Default>

c0000100
00:05:19.360 --> 00:05:22.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I guess it's like--
I feel like it's a bit unfair.</b></Default>

c0000101
00:05:23.240 --> 00:05:24.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Unfair?</b></Default>

c0000102
00:05:24.570 --> 00:05:26.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- If the roles were reversed
with this,</b></Default>

c0000103
00:05:26.790 --> 00:05:29.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and she said she was planning
to go meet her first crush,</b></Default>

c0000104
00:05:29.330 --> 00:05:31.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>it would definitely mess
with my head.</b></Default>

c0000105
00:05:31.460 --> 00:05:34.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Sakurajima's not that kind
of person, though, right?</b></Default>

c0000106
00:05:34.080 --> 00:05:36.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She's the type that when
presented with a problem</b></Default>

c0000107
00:05:36.130 --> 00:05:37.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>always faces it head-on.</b></Default>

c0000108
00:05:37.670 --> 00:05:39.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- That's true.
[cell phone vibrating]</b></Default>

c0000109
00:05:39.340 --> 00:05:41.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey, what have you been doing
this whole time?</b></Default>

c0000110
00:05:41.630 --> 00:05:43.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You're being
unfathomably tedious</b></Default>

c0000111
00:05:43.550 --> 00:05:45.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so I've been texting
your girlfriend</b></Default>

c0000112
00:05:45.140 --> 00:05:46.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>everything you've said.
- What?</b></Default>

c0000113
00:05:47.010 --> 00:05:48.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- She said she'll be right over.</b></Default>

c0000114
00:05:48.310 --> 00:05:50.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Hold on! Hey!
- So, yeah. Enjoy.</b></Default>

c0000115
00:05:52.440 --> 00:05:55.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Thanks for the info, Futaba.
- No problem. 'Scuse me.</b></Default>

c0000116
00:05:57.690 --> 00:05:58.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[door slides closed]</b></Default>

c0000117
00:05:58.900 --> 00:06:00.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- So, Sakuta.</b></Default>

c0000118
00:06:00.780 --> 00:06:02.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Hey. Yes, what is it?</b></Default>

c0000119
00:06:02.950 --> 00:06:05.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Think you could get back home
by 6:00 o'clock?</b></Default>

c0000120
00:06:05.200 --> 00:06:07.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Huh?
- I'll come over and make dinner</b></Default>

c0000121
00:06:07.120 --> 00:06:08.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>for you.
- Y--uh, yes.</b></Default>

c0000122
00:06:08.740 --> 00:06:10.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think I can get back by then.</b></Default>

c0000123
00:06:10.660 --> 00:06:13.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Good. I'll swing by your place
around that time.</b></Default>

c0000124
00:06:13.580 --> 00:06:15.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [groans]</b></Default>

c0000125
00:06:17.040 --> 00:06:19.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, uh, is that all, Mai?</b></Default>

c0000126
00:06:19.960 --> 00:06:22.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- What's this? You want me
to act all jealous or something?</b></Default>

c0000127
00:06:22.550 --> 00:06:24.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Well, there's that, but--</b></Default>

c0000128
00:06:24.680 --> 00:06:27.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I don't know exactly how
to put this into words,</b></Default>

c0000129
00:06:27.640 --> 00:06:29.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but I can't say that
I'm not curious, too.</b></Default>

c0000130
00:06:30.640 --> 00:06:32.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Shoko-san and Shoko-chan--</b></Default>

c0000131
00:06:32.640 --> 00:06:35.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>how can you not wonder
how they're related?</b></Default>

c0000132
00:06:35.560 --> 00:06:37.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- So that's why
you're forgiving me.</b></Default>

c0000133
00:06:37.440 --> 00:06:38.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is that right?</b></Default>

c0000134
00:06:38.650 --> 00:06:40.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- She is the person
who supported you</b></Default>

c0000135
00:06:40.480 --> 00:06:42.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>when you were going through
that depression.</b></Default>

c0000136
00:06:42.150 --> 00:06:44.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So for me it's that
I don't want you to have</b></Default>

c0000137
00:06:44.780 --> 00:06:46.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>some weird
lingering regret about her.</b></Default>

c0000138
00:06:47.120 --> 00:06:48.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Though I find none of this fun.</b></Default>

c0000139
00:06:48.740 --> 00:06:50.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [grunts]</b></Default>

c0000140
00:06:50.660 --> 00:06:51.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Have any thoughts?</b></Default>

c0000141
00:06:55.210 --> 00:06:57.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Hey, Mai!
I love you!</b></Default>

c0000142
00:06:57.710 --> 00:06:59.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You're embarrassing me!
Stop it!</b></Default>

c0000143
00:06:59.670 --> 00:07:02.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Show me how sincere you
are in a different way!</b></Default>

c0000144
00:07:02.210 --> 00:07:03.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Okay, I
will.</b></Default>

c0000145
00:07:05.930 --> 00:07:07.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ow, what was that for?</b></Default>

c0000146
00:07:07.840 --> 00:07:10.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Explain to me why I should
have to kiss a boyfriend</b></Default>

c0000147
00:07:10.180 --> 00:07:12.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that is about to go meet up
with his previous crush.</b></Default>

c0000148
00:07:12.350 --> 00:07:15.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I thought you just gave me
permission to do that earlier.</b></Default>

c0000149
00:07:15.100 --> 00:07:17.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- This is this
and that is that.</b></Default>

c0000150
00:07:17.150 --> 00:07:20.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I might allow it but I won't let
it be that easy.</b></Default>

c0000151
00:07:20.520 --> 00:07:23.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[school bell ringing]</b></Default>

c0000152
00:07:23.230 --> 00:07:25.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Well, as I promised, I will
definitely make sure to be home</b></Default>

c0000153
00:07:25.650 --> 00:07:26.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>by 6:00 o'clock.</b></Default>

c0000154
00:07:26.860 --> 00:07:27.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]
- [grunts]</b></Default>

c0000155
00:07:28.950 --> 00:07:31.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hello.
- Uh, do you remember me?</b></Default>

c0000156
00:07:32.040 --> 00:07:33.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm Kotomi Kano,</b></Default>

c0000157
00:07:33.580 --> 00:07:35.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>one of Kae's
childhood friends.</b></Default>

c0000158
00:07:35.160 --> 00:07:36.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Oh.</b></Default>

c0000159
00:07:36.960 --> 00:07:39.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- How 'bout chatting
somewhere else?</b></Default>

c0000160
00:07:39.380 --> 00:07:40.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I'm so sorry.</b></Default>

c0000161
00:07:40.920 --> 00:07:43.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm sure I'm troubling you
showing up so suddenly.</b></Default>

c0000162
00:07:43.250 --> 00:07:45.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- No, don't even worry about it.
You're totally fine.</b></Default>

c0000163
00:07:46.220 --> 00:07:49.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Uh, Mai, it's terribly hard
for me to ask this, but--</b></Default>

c0000164
00:07:49.510 --> 00:07:50.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [exhales sharply]</b></Default>

c0000165
00:07:50.640 --> 00:07:52.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes, I'll go to the beach
for you.</b></Default>

c0000166
00:07:52.720 --> 00:07:55.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Since I know Shoko-chan,
I'd recognize her easily, right?</b></Default>

c0000167
00:07:55.890 --> 00:07:57.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Yes, it shouldn't be hard.</b></Default>

c0000168
00:07:59.400 --> 00:08:02.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I'm so sorry for interrupting
your plans.</b></Default>

c0000169
00:08:02.940 --> 00:08:04.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- It's okay.
Question, though.</b></Default>

c0000170
00:08:05.030 --> 00:08:07.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How'd you figure out which
high school I go to?</b></Default>

c0000171
00:08:07.150 --> 00:08:10.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Well, I--I saw you in
a magazine.</b></Default>

c0000172
00:08:10.620 --> 00:08:11.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Oh.</b></Default>

c0000173
00:08:11.990 --> 00:08:14.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I was trying to forget
this whole time.</b></Default>

c0000174
00:08:14.580 --> 00:08:16.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Ah?
- Such terrible things happened</b></Default>

c0000175
00:08:16.870 --> 00:08:19.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to Kae and I couldn't
do anything to help.</b></Default>

c0000176
00:08:20.040 --> 00:08:22.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Soon after the two
of you moved away together.</b></Default>

c0000177
00:08:22.420 --> 00:08:25.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [grunts]
- And then once you were gone,</b></Default>

c0000178
00:08:25.130 --> 00:08:28.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the bullying against Kae became
a huge problem at school.</b></Default>

c0000179
00:08:28.550 --> 00:08:31.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The girls who bullied her
were ostracized for it.</b></Default>

c0000180
00:08:31.090 --> 00:08:33.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Everyone started telling them
they should disappear</b></Default>

c0000181
00:08:33.430 --> 00:08:34.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>or just die.</b></Default>

c0000182
00:08:35.060 --> 00:08:38.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So eventually those girls
stopped coming to school, too.</b></Default>

c0000183
00:08:38.730 --> 00:08:40.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It started to feel like
we all defeated the villain</b></Default>

c0000184
00:08:40.730 --> 00:08:42.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and it was finally over.</b></Default>

c0000185
00:08:43.190 --> 00:08:45.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I see.
- But still, I--</b></Default>

c0000186
00:08:45.400 --> 00:08:47.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I wasn't able to do anything
for Kae.</b></Default>

c0000187
00:08:48.280 --> 00:08:50.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I couldn't protect her from it.</b></Default>

c0000188
00:08:50.410 --> 00:08:52.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>All I did was worry about her.</b></Default>

c0000189
00:08:52.450 --> 00:08:53.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- It's not your fault.</b></Default>

c0000190
00:08:53.830 --> 00:08:54.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You couldn't really do anything</b></Default>

c0000191
00:08:54.950 --> 00:08:56.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>from the classroom next door.</b></Default>

c0000192
00:08:56.450 --> 00:08:57.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- So, uh...</b></Default>

c0000193
00:08:57.950 --> 00:08:59.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Has Kae been doing well?</b></Default>

c0000194
00:08:59.620 --> 00:09:01.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Yeah, she has.</b></Default>

c0000195
00:09:01.250 --> 00:09:02.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Though she loves our house
so much,</b></Default>

c0000196
00:09:02.960 --> 00:09:04.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>she can't bring herself
to leave it.</b></Default>

c0000197
00:09:04.460 --> 00:09:05.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [groans]</b></Default>

c0000198
00:09:05.800 --> 00:09:07.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- There's no reason to dwell
on it, Kano.</b></Default>

c0000199
00:09:08.420 --> 00:09:10.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Is it possible for me
to see Kae?</b></Default>

c0000200
00:09:10.430 --> 00:09:11.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [grunts]</b></Default>

c0000201
00:09:11.630 --> 00:09:13.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It might confuse her.</b></Default>

c0000202
00:09:16.640 --> 00:09:18.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Sorry, Mai.
Here now.</b></Default>

c0000203
00:09:18.350 --> 00:09:19.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Where's the girl?</b></Default>

c0000204
00:09:19.520 --> 00:09:21.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I took her to
the train station.</b></Default>

c0000205
00:09:21.310 --> 00:09:23.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Then I guess I'm done.
I'll head back first.</b></Default>

c0000206
00:09:23.730 --> 00:09:25.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I'll go home now, too.</b></Default>

c0000207
00:09:25.940 --> 00:09:27.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You aren't going to wait
for Shoko-san?</b></Default>

c0000208
00:09:27.650 --> 00:09:29.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- The sun is setting soon.</b></Default>

c0000209
00:09:29.360 --> 00:09:31.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So even if she showed,
I probably wouldn't notice.</b></Default>

c0000210
00:09:32.070 --> 00:09:33.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- As long as you're okay
with it,</b></Default>

c0000211
00:09:33.530 --> 00:09:35.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm okay with it.
- [exhales sharply]</b></Default>

c0000212
00:09:35.280 --> 00:09:36.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But I guess I should tell her
what I've been wanting</b></Default>

c0000213
00:09:36.910 --> 00:09:37.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to tell her.</b></Default>

c0000214
00:09:46.460 --> 00:09:48.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [chuckles]</b></Default>

c0000215
00:09:48.250 --> 00:09:49.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[door creaks]
- Big brother!</b></Default>

c0000216
00:09:49.960 --> 00:09:51.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Dinner's gonna be
a little later.</b></Default>

c0000217
00:09:51.970 --> 00:09:54.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mai is going to be coming over
to cook for us tonight.</b></Default>

c0000218
00:09:54.430 --> 00:09:57.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Her meals are always tasty.
I'm looking forward to it!</b></Default>

c0000219
00:09:57.970 --> 00:09:59.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But before Kaede can think
about that,</b></Default>

c0000220
00:09:59.930 --> 00:10:01.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>she has an important
announcement to make.</b></Default>

c0000221
00:10:01.680 --> 00:10:02.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Uh?</b></Default>

c0000222
00:10:03.310 --> 00:10:04.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Ta-dah!</b></Default>

c0000223
00:10:04.980 --> 00:10:05.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Hmm.</b></Default>

c0000224
00:10:07.320 --> 00:10:08.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What am I looking at?</b></Default>

c0000225
00:10:08.820 --> 00:10:11.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- These are all of Kaede's goals
for this year.</b></Default>

c0000226
00:10:12.650 --> 00:10:14.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- We're gonna mingle?
- We will indeed.</b></Default>

c0000227
00:10:17.080 --> 00:10:18.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Hey, Kaede.</b></Default>

c0000228
00:10:18.540 --> 00:10:19.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- What is it?</b></Default>

c0000229
00:10:19.950 --> 00:10:21.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Isn't there anything
that doesn't involve me?</b></Default>

c0000230
00:10:21.960 --> 00:10:23.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Yeah, here.
This one.</b></Default>

c0000231
00:10:25.540 --> 00:10:26.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [grunts]</b></Default>

c0000232
00:10:26.540 --> 00:10:27.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000233
00:10:28.340 --> 00:10:29.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Well, big brother?</b></Default>

c0000234
00:10:29.340 --> 00:10:30.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What do you think?</b></Default>

c0000235
00:10:30.760 --> 00:10:34.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- First off, don't you have
too many goals?</b></Default>

c0000236
00:10:34.180 --> 00:10:36.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There's only two and a half
months left in the year.</b></Default>

c0000237
00:10:36.140 --> 00:10:39.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Also, the leap between answering
the phone and going to school</b></Default>

c0000238
00:10:39.220 --> 00:10:41.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is too big.
Best not to overdo it.</b></Default>

c0000239
00:10:41.680 --> 00:10:43.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Yeah, good point.
Hmm.</b></Default>

c0000240
00:10:43.890 --> 00:10:46.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Stepping outside might be
a bit too hard right now.</b></Default>

c0000241
00:10:46.270 --> 00:10:47.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- In the meantime,</b></Default>

c0000242
00:10:47.560 --> 00:10:48.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>how about coming up
with some goals</b></Default>

c0000243
00:10:48.860 --> 00:10:50.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that make you actually want
to go out?</b></Default>

c0000244
00:10:50.860 --> 00:10:53.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Can you give me an example?
- Let's see.</b></Default>

c0000245
00:10:53.530 --> 00:10:55.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Like going to see pandas?</b></Default>

c0000246
00:10:55.110 --> 00:10:57.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Pandas?
You mean like giant pandas?</b></Default>

c0000247
00:10:57.700 --> 00:10:59.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- We could also go see
the lesser pandas</b></Default>

c0000248
00:10:59.580 --> 00:11:01.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>if you want to.
- I wanna see 'em all!</b></Default>

c0000249
00:11:04.210 --> 00:11:06.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[giggles]
Perfect!</b></Default>

c0000250
00:11:06.250 --> 00:11:08.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Now Kaede feels going outside
is possible!</b></Default>

c0000251
00:11:12.800 --> 00:11:15.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chomping]</b></Default>

c0000252
00:11:15.180 --> 00:11:16.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The yellow tail's so juicy!</b></Default>

c0000253
00:11:17.010 --> 00:11:19.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're such a good cook, Mai.
Amazing!</b></Default>

c0000254
00:11:19.720 --> 00:11:21.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- If you put in the practice,</b></Default>

c0000255
00:11:21.220 --> 00:11:23.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you'll be able to make
it like this as well.</b></Default>

c0000256
00:11:23.100 --> 00:11:24.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You think so?</b></Default>

c0000257
00:11:24.480 --> 00:11:25.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[phone ringing]
[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000258
00:11:28.730 --> 00:11:30.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Azusagawa residence.</b></Default>

c0000259
00:11:30.400 --> 00:11:33.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Um, it's Makinohara.
Good evening.</b></Default>

c0000260
00:11:33.650 --> 00:11:35.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Hi. Good evening to you.</b></Default>

c0000261
00:11:35.450 --> 00:11:37.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I wanted to apologize.</b></Default>

c0000262
00:11:37.320 --> 00:11:39.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm sorry that it took me
so long to get back to you</b></Default>

c0000263
00:11:39.320 --> 00:11:40.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>after you called me yesterday.</b></Default>

c0000264
00:11:40.620 --> 00:11:41.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- No worries.</b></Default>

c0000265
00:11:41.740 --> 00:11:42.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I just had something I wanted</b></Default>

c0000266
00:11:42.910 --> 00:11:44.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to confirm with you.</b></Default>

c0000267
00:11:44.700 --> 00:11:47.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Uh, Makinohara, did you happen
to put a letter in our mailbox?</b></Default>

c0000268
00:11:48.120 --> 00:11:51.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- A letter? No.
- I see. All good, then.</b></Default>

c0000269
00:11:52.000 --> 00:11:54.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You haven't been
coming over much.</b></Default>

c0000270
00:11:54.170 --> 00:11:56.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Have you been okay?
- Yes. I'm sorry.</b></Default>

c0000271
00:11:56.970 --> 00:11:59.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've left Hayate in your care
for all this time, too.</b></Default>

c0000272
00:11:59.930 --> 00:12:01.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Did something happen?
- No.</b></Default>

c0000273
00:12:02.060 --> 00:12:04.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I just haven't been feeling
very well lately.</b></Default>

c0000274
00:12:04.640 --> 00:12:07.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll start visiting again once
I'm feeling a bit better.</b></Default>

c0000275
00:12:07.640 --> 00:12:09.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [grunts]
That sounds good.</b></Default>

c0000276
00:12:14.190 --> 00:12:16.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- U--um, big brother?
- Hmm?</b></Default>

c0000277
00:12:16.950 --> 00:12:19.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- If Shoko calls us on
the house phone again,</b></Default>

c0000278
00:12:19.410 --> 00:12:21.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>then can Kaede pick
it up next time?</b></Default>

c0000279
00:12:21.820 --> 00:12:25.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Sure. That's fine.
- Kaede, you want to answer it?</b></Default>

c0000280
00:12:26.000 --> 00:12:28.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Yes. That is one
of Kaede's goals!</b></Default>

c0000281
00:12:28.750 --> 00:12:31.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You're serious.
Did something happen?</b></Default>

c0000282
00:12:31.920 --> 00:12:34.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Kaede came to a realization.</b></Default>

c0000283
00:12:34.380 --> 00:12:36.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If she isn't able to live
on her own one day,</b></Default>

c0000284
00:12:37.010 --> 00:12:39.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>big brother will never be able
to marry in his whole life.</b></Default>

c0000285
00:12:39.630 --> 00:12:41.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You care to elaborate?</b></Default>

c0000286
00:12:41.510 --> 00:12:44.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-
Because whoever marries
big brother will also get Kaede.</b></Default>

c0000287
00:12:44.680 --> 00:12:46.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's a two-for-one combo!
- [grunts]</b></Default>

c0000288
00:12:47.390 --> 00:12:49.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm certain that Mai will
be happy to have you.</b></Default>

c0000289
00:12:49.850 --> 00:12:52.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- It's true. I wouldn't mind
having you around at all.</b></Default>

c0000290
00:12:52.860 --> 00:12:55.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But then again, I think you
wanting to be independent</b></Default>

c0000291
00:12:55.730 --> 00:12:56.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is a good thing.</b></Default>

c0000292
00:12:56.940 --> 00:12:58.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do you want
to practice answering</b></Default>

c0000293
00:12:58.490 --> 00:13:00.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the phone with me right now?
- [gasps]</b></Default>

c0000294
00:13:02.280 --> 00:13:03.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasping]</b></Default>

c0000295
00:13:05.580 --> 00:13:06.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[phone rings]
[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000296
00:13:06.580 --> 00:13:08.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- It's okay.
It's Mai.</b></Default>

c0000297
00:13:08.330 --> 00:13:09.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]
Okay.</b></Default>

c0000298
00:13:10.420 --> 00:13:12.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[whimpering]</b></Default>

c0000299
00:13:12.380 --> 00:13:13.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000300
00:13:13.840 --> 00:13:15.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A--Azusagawa here!</b></Default>

c0000301
00:13:15.800 --> 00:13:17.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Congratulations, Kaede.</b></Default>

c0000302
00:13:17.550 --> 00:13:19.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You did so good.</b></Default>

c0000303
00:13:19.170 --> 00:13:21.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Hey, big brother!
It worked!</b></Default>

c0000304
00:13:21.180 --> 00:13:23.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Hello? Kaede,
can you hear me over there?</b></Default>

c0000305
00:13:23.680 --> 00:13:25.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Y--Yes! Loud and clear!</b></Default>

c0000306
00:13:26.720 --> 00:13:28.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Looks like you'll be able
to answer calls for me now.</b></Default>

c0000307
00:13:29.020 --> 00:13:30.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I'm proud of you.
Good job.</b></Default>

c0000308
00:13:30.600 --> 00:13:32.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]
- Kaede!</b></Default>

c0000309
00:13:33.350 --> 00:13:34.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- It's no big deal.</b></Default>

c0000310
00:13:34.690 --> 00:13:35.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[both gasping]</b></Default>

c0000311
00:13:35.820 --> 00:13:37.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She has a fever.</b></Default>

c0000312
00:13:37.360 --> 00:13:39.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Sorry. I pushed you
to do too much.</b></Default>

c0000313
00:13:39.780 --> 00:13:41.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Oh, no.
Thanks to your help,</b></Default>

c0000314
00:13:41.780 --> 00:13:44.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Kaede was able to complete one
of her big goals already.</b></Default>

c0000315
00:13:44.780 --> 00:13:48.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>At this pace going outside may
be possible tomorrow, too!</b></Default>

c0000316
00:13:48.200 --> 00:13:49.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Yeah, maybe so.</b></Default>

c0000317
00:13:49.700 --> 00:13:51.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Then we could go see
the pandas.</b></Default>

c0000318
00:13:51.580 --> 00:13:52.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[giggles]</b></Default>

c0000319
00:13:53.370 --> 00:13:56.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[breathing deeply</b></Default>

c0000320
00:13:56.420 --> 00:13:59.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[dramatic piano music]</b></Default>

c0000321
