<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000487
00:20:44.990 --> 00:20:46.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Big brother?</b></Default>

c0000488
00:20:46.450 --> 00:20:48.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Isn't this--
- Yep, outside.</b></Default>

c0000489
00:20:48.790 --> 00:20:51.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Th--then was this all
a part of your scheme?</b></Default>

c0000490
00:20:52.040 --> 00:20:53.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Yeah, it was.</b></Default>

c0000491
00:20:53.960 --> 00:20:55.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [whimpers]
Kaede is...</b></Default>

c0000492
00:20:56.420 --> 00:20:59.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[crying]
- Hey, Kaede.</b></Default>

c0000493
00:20:59.680 --> 00:21:02.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm so sorry
for tricking you like that.</b></Default>

c0000494
00:21:02.180 --> 00:21:05.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Big brother!
Big brother, you--</b></Default>

c0000495
00:21:05.600 --> 00:21:07.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I'm sorry.
I really am.</b></Default>

c0000496
00:21:07.730 --> 00:21:09.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- No! That's not it!</b></Default>

c0000497
00:21:09.520 --> 00:21:11.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's not it!</b></Default>

c0000498
00:21:11.150 --> 00:21:12.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Kaede is...</b></Default>

c0000499
00:21:13.110 --> 00:21:14.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Kaede is outside!</b></Default>

c0000500
00:21:14.940 --> 00:21:17.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She's so happy that she made
it outside!</b></Default>

c0000501
00:21:17.190 --> 00:21:19.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[crying]
- [gasps]</b></Default>

c0000502
00:21:19.490 --> 00:21:23.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [wailing]</b></Default>

c0000503
00:21:24.530 --> 00:21:27.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Since then Kaede's been able
to venture further</b></Default>

c0000504
00:21:27.370 --> 00:21:28.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and further outside.</b></Default>

c0000505
00:21:29.210 --> 00:21:31.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The next day she made it
to the elevator.</b></Default>

c0000506
00:21:32.540 --> 00:21:35.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b> And the day after that she made
it to the building entrance</b></Default>

c0000507
00:21:35.130 --> 00:21:36.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>on the first floor.</b></Default>

c0000508
00:21:37.210 --> 00:21:39.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It was smooth sailing
from there.</b></Default>

c0000509
00:21:39.090 --> 00:21:40.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She managed to eat over
at Mai's place</b></Default>

c0000510
00:21:40.970 --> 00:21:42.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and even hang out at
the local park.</b></Default>

c0000511
00:21:44.050 --> 00:21:45.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Oh, Azusagawa.</b></Default>

c0000512
00:21:45.930 --> 00:21:47.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You sister-obsessed rascal.</b></Default>

c0000513
00:21:47.640 --> 00:21:49.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- What are you going on about?</b></Default>

c0000514
00:21:49.310 --> 00:21:51.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- A second-year high school boy
talking this much about</b></Default>

c0000515
00:21:51.600 --> 00:21:52.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>his little sister
is ample reason</b></Default>

c0000516
00:21:53.020 --> 00:21:55.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to call him sister-obsessed.
- You think so?</b></Default>

c0000517
00:21:55.560 --> 00:21:58.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Well, in any case,
I really am glad to hear it.</b></Default>

c0000518
00:21:58.940 --> 00:22:01.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Thank you.
- By the way,</b></Default>

c0000519
00:22:01.450 --> 00:22:03.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>have you had the chance to talk
to Sakurajima yet?</b></Default>

c0000520
00:22:03.990 --> 00:22:05.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Huh? Talk about what?</b></Default>

c0000521
00:22:05.870 --> 00:22:07.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- The thing that's going on
with Kaede.</b></Default>

c0000522
00:22:08.990 --> 00:22:10.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [grunts]</b></Default>

c0000523
00:22:10.290 --> 00:22:11.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Ah, so you haven't.</b></Default>

c0000524
00:22:16.590 --> 00:22:19.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You sure they don't
all think Kaede is weird?</b></Default>

c0000525
00:22:19.380 --> 00:22:20.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You're totally fine.</b></Default>

c0000526
00:22:20.760 --> 00:22:22.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Kaede feels
a few judgy glances</b></Default>

c0000527
00:22:22.930 --> 00:22:23.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>in this direction, though.</b></Default>

c0000528
00:22:23.930 --> 00:22:25.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- That's probably because you've</b></Default>

c0000529
00:22:25.510 --> 00:22:27.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>been latched onto me like
a koala bear.</b></Default>

c0000530
00:22:27.680 --> 00:22:29.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Maybe, but if Kaede were
to let go,</b></Default>

c0000531
00:22:29.890 --> 00:22:31.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>she would certainly die.
- [exhales]</b></Default>

c0000532
00:22:32.270 --> 00:22:34.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Kaede, look outside
the window behind you.</b></Default>

c0000533
00:22:35.810 --> 00:22:36.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [grunts]</b></Default>

c0000534
00:22:41.650 --> 00:22:43.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]
It's the ocean!</b></Default>

c0000535
00:22:50.580 --> 00:22:53.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Onigiri you eat outside
are really something else.</b></Default>

c0000536
00:22:54.120 --> 00:22:55.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Yeah, they are.</b></Default>

c0000537
00:22:55.210 --> 00:22:56.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But it's more like the onigiri</b></Default>

c0000538
00:22:56.540 --> 00:22:57.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mai makes are something else.</b></Default>

c0000539
00:22:57.750 --> 00:22:58.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Just so you know,</b></Default>

c0000540
00:22:58.750 --> 00:22:59.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I was the one who made</b></Default>

c0000541
00:22:59.920 --> 00:23:01.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the salmon filling
you're eating.</b></Default>

c0000542
00:23:01.340 --> 00:23:03.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- No wonder they aren't as--
- Then don't eat 'em!</b></Default>

