00:23:11.350 --> 00:23:12.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[both laughing]</b></Default>

c0000546
00:23:12.520 --> 00:23:13.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [grunts]</b></Default>

c0000547
